quran[9{c,v,t}:
30,42,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho ke zameen mein chal phir kar dekho pehlay guzray hue logon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai, un mein se aksar mushriq hi thay"
30,43,pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) apna rukh mazbooti ke sath jama do iss deen raast ki simt mein qabal is ke ke woh din aeye jis ke tal jaane ki koi soorat Allah ki taraf se nahi hai uss din log phatt kar aik doosray se allag ho jayen ge
30,44,jis ne kufar kya hai is ke kufar ka wabaal isi par hai aur jin logon ne naik amal kya hai woh apne hi liye Falah ka rasta saaf kar rahay hain
30,45,taakay Allah imaan laane walon aur Amal Saleh karne walon ko apne fazl se jaza day yaqeenan woh kafiroon ko pasand nahi karta
30,46,uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke woh hawae bhejta hai basharat dainay ke liye aur tumhe apni rehmat se behra mand karne ke liye aur is gharz ke liye ke kashtiyan is ke hukum se chalein aur tum is ka fazl talaash karo aur is ke shukar guzaar bano
30,47,"aur hum ne tum se pehlay Rasolo-n ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja aur woh un ke paas roshan nishanain le kar aeye, phir jinhon ne jurm kya unn se hum ne intiqam liya aur hum par yeh haq tha ke hum mominon ki madad karen"
30,48,"Allah hi hai jo hawaon ko bhejta hai aur woh baadal athati hain, phir woh inn baadalon ko aasman mein phela deta hai jis terhan chahta hai aur inhen tkrhyon mein taqseem karta hai, phir too daikhta hai ke barish ke qatray baadal se tpke chalay atay hain yeh barish jab woh apne bundon mein se jin par chahta hai barsata hai"
30,49,to yakayak woh khush o Khurram ho jatay hain halaank is ke nuzool se pehlay woh mayoos ho rahay thay
30,50,"dekho Allah ki rehmat ke asraat ke murda pari hui zameen ko woh kis terhan jِla uthata hai, yaqeenan woh mُrdon ko zindagi bakhsnay wala hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
